reviewText: My brother is a huge fan of the Flying Walenda's and for the past couple of years has been taking his kids to Circus Flora. This was the perfect Christmas Gift for him!

This is a fascinating documentary of a small one ring circus based in St. Louis, MO. The main reason to get this tape is to see the Wallenda family re-create the seven person pyramid on the tight wire...it it spell binding to see this act again. Wish Circus Flora would play New York City with the Flying Wallenda family.
